            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Asian-style salad</strong> topped with the <strong>pulled hoisin duck </strong>and <strong>sesame croutons</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>hoisin dressing</strong> and garnish with the <strong>remaining toasted sesame seeds </strong>and<strong> black sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
